data.description: Welcome to 5440 Manor Park Drive. This lovely updated home offers both comfort and style, perfect for families seeking a cozy retreat in a thriving community. Boasting 4 bedrooms and  2 1/2 bathrooms, this spacious home offers usable space for your family to grow and thrive. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring sleek countertops, butcher block island, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of storage space for all your culinary needs. Relax and unwind in the cozy living room with fireplace and large windows that flood the space with natural light. Entertain in the dining room or utilize it as a home office. Retreat to the elegant oversized primary suite, featuring a spa-like ensuite bathroom with a separate tub and shower and a walk-in closet for added convenience. Finishing the upstairs are 3 secondary bedrooms and a full sized bath. Step outside to discover a fenced private backyard oasis, perfect for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying a quiet afternoon under the sun. Located in a family-friendly neighborhood with swim and tennis as well as access to top-rated schools, parks, and recreational facilities. Conveniently situated near shopping, dining, and entertainment options, ensuring you'll never have a dull moment.
